{"tid":359904,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"LG 被指偷竊藝術家作品製作手機 Wallpaper","createTime":"2017-08-15T00:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T00:14:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e15231d335857d233420e75a9723207fa958529","tid":359904,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:22:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">巴西當代藝術家 Lygia Pape 的女兒指控 LG，指他們在未經授權下使用母親的裝置藝術作品《Tteia 1, C》，作為手機 K20V 的 Wallpaper。這個藝術作品而金絲線製作，LG 曾經嘗試和 Lygia Pape 的基金會洽談使用許可但遭到拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後因為產品上市時間緊迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，LG 在未經授權下就將藝術品使用在手機 Wallpaper 和廣告宣傳上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/081834_bac96b64d3cb01da0d73c33beeb09a1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F081834_bac96b64d3cb01da0d73c33beeb09a1f.jpg&h=51232c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/08/14/lg-k20v-wallpaper-problem/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F08%2F14%2Flg-k20v-wallpaper-problem%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=5r9K3LpCLxi7ws6UocUQQV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=56423eae\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/08/14/lg-k20v-wallpaper-problem/mobile-phone/</a></div>"},{"pid":"fd757f945bc0453ea9cc5d87d22eb286246276e6","tid":359904,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:25:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/082403_169c6346acbafbc6f42e09f78798813d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F082403_169c6346acbafbc6f42e09f78798813d.jpg&h=5b306e16&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n現時問題不單是 LG 剽竊了藝術家的作品，還對藝術家極不尊重，因為 Pape 的女兒指母親在 50 年的創作期間，從不將創作用作商業用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，亦不會以藝術品涉及任何商業或牟利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Pape 的女兒現時興訟，要求 LG 公開藝術家的身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同時銷毀未經授權的藝術品翻作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，由於 LG 將之用於手機的軟件和包裝，假如訴訟成立，LG 可能需要召回所有手機和撤回產品的廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n來源：artobserved"},{"pid":"ef0b23f04d78fb1019f5d10fe9f5cccce8b1c1ec","tid":359904,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:26:08.000Z","msg":"死韓狗"},{"pid":"ba88dcdb91fb6d8c16cb9ea8d3bb103b9836b000","tid":359904,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b15cb07fa21bebbc8bceb280fb65b6bc274ce86","tid":359904,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66bb1fd2d3e9b9c88384cce3607b5627111f8ab","tid":359904,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而金絲線製作<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>以金絲線製作</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XbZCs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXbZCs.png&h=90b16d4b&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n無處不在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f12b0a799c35b41cfd369b79586e7a571e775c","tid":359904,"uid":3180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:02:27.000Z","msg":"邊忽似 金色就話係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd82b31fd483d0867fdacfe2c9512c629c1fbeb","tid":359904,"uid":112128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊忽似 金色就話係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">LG 曾經嘗試和 Lygia Pape 的基金會洽談使用許可但遭到拒絕</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你覺得唔似啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係LG真係抄咗喎，唔係使鬼問人拎授權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e7c222f487bf70c04b6b292c1b447e4e5d76e1","tid":359904,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:10:41.000Z","msg":"除左金線之外仲有咩共通點？"},{"pid":"ccad8bb2448fdb111fa4402aa1204aa00c83a322","tid":359904,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n有咩似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7301d6c16200efd4d6b7798e8cd8030eb6a31b3","tid":359904,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"呢張都仲ok<br />\n今次v30張正面圖就真係抄得厚面皮啦"},{"pid":"1294f23b69c090c2d9aab0d8054020d6c930e996","tid":359904,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"但係真係唔似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7db09262c1893c27ab3ebf0d0470c292b9e67d0","tid":359904,"uid":16904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"問完唔得都仲要抄"},{"pid":"d4d412788d2f1c7244a611c6c0df6f9b8d886278","tid":359904,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/082403_169c6346acbafbc6f42e09f78798813d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F082403_169c6346acbafbc6f42e09f78798813d.jpg&h=5b306e16&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：artobserved</blockquote><br />\nlg出咗部iphone？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91fbfc0418de25c032ba501b3b28fed05aaadbd","tid":359904,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/082403_169c6346acbafbc6f42e09f78798813d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F082403_169c6346acbafbc6f42e09f78798813d.jpg&h=5b306e16&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：artobserved</blockquote><br />\nlg出咗部iphone？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3e4d258119f1d3630b73c212bbebb9bc02fe32","tid":359904,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}